;;
;; [ completely       ]
;; [ undifferentiated ]
;; [ instructions     ]
;;        |
;;     compress-
;;   instructions
;;        |
;;        v
;; [ baskets of instrs     ]
;; [ which act on over-    ]
;; [ lapping sets of qubits]
